&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Facilities Department – Uniform Services – Evesham Community Hospital &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Administrator – Uniform Services&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 3&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;25 Hours per week – Fixed Term Contract for 12 Months &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to work within a busy and varied environment, working alongsideour clinical and other non-clinical colleagues to make a positive contribution to our patients and staff experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is specifically assigned to uniform services/ provision, and will provide a fully managed administration role in the ordering, procurement and supply of uniforms to all Trust staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Benefits include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NHS pension&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dedicated training&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Progression and apprenticeship opportunities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Generous annual leave allowance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information please contact Emily Packwood on 01905 681486.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;All staff whatever their role, level or responsibility will be encouraged and supported to do their job well and to improve their job.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Making Every Day Better for patients, staff, service users and carers is the responsibility of all of us and we want to embed a culture within the organisation that encourages and supports the drive to improve what we do.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications for this role will be considered in adherence with the Working Time Regulations policy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
